---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="bg-[#FF5900] text-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-10">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold mb-3">Teman Ngobrol</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          Komunitas mahasiswa untuk kuliah ke luar negeri — info beasiswa, biaya hidup, dan cerita nyata dari perantauan.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-body font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 text-white/60">Tautan</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/" class="font-body text-sm text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors no-underline">Beranda</a></li>
          <li><a href="/articles" class="font-body text-sm text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors no-underline">Artikel</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="font-body text-sm text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors no-underline">Tentang Kami</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-body font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 text-white/60">Ikuti Kami</h4>
        <a
          href="https://instagram.com/temanngobrol"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-body text-sm text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors no-underline"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/>
          </svg>
          @temanngobrol
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-white/20 pt-6 text-center">
      <p class="font-body text-sm text-white/60">
        &copy; {today.getFullYear()} Teman Ngobrol. Dibuat dengan ❤️ oleh mahasiswa, untuk mahasiswa.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
